headline: 2 Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Skip, and 1 You Should Buy for Income
summary: Enbridge backs its high-yielding payout with very stable cash flow.  Ford's free cash flow was already on track to fall even before the impact of tariffs.  UPS's free cash flow has also felt the impact of tariffs.
